01:02:55.563 --> 01:02:58.984
<i>♪ And so it never dies ♪</i>

749
01:03:00.068 --> 01:03:02.612
<i>♪ There's a perfect world ♪</i>

750
01:03:03.905 --> 01:03:07.242
<i>♪ Shining in your eyes ♪</i>

751
01:03:08.785 --> 01:03:12.497
<i>♪ And if only they could feel it, too ♪</i>

752
01:03:12.789 --> 01:03:16.251
<i>♪ The happiness I feel with you ♪</i>

753
01:03:16.376 --> 01:03:18.378
<i>♪ They'd know ♪</i>

754
01:03:18.712 --> 01:03:22.007
<i>♪ Love will find a way ♪</i>

755
01:03:22.507 --> 01:03:25.427
<i>♪ Anywhere we go ♪</i>

756
01:03:25.510 --> 01:03:31.391
<i>♪ We're home ♪
♪ if we are there together ♪</i>

757
01:03:31.474 --> 01:03:36.354
<i>♪ Like dark turning into day ♪</i>

758
01:03:37.564 --> 01:03:40.984
<i>♪ Somehow we'll come through ♪</i>

759
01:03:41.318 --> 01:03:44.279
<i>♪ Now that I've found you ♪</i>

760
01:03:45.071 --> 01:03:47.907
<i>♪ Love will find a way ♪</i>

761
01:03:49.200 --> 01:03:51.494
<i>♪ I know ♪</i>

762
01:03:51.578 --> 01:03:58.293
<i>♪ Love will find a way ♪</i>

763
01:04:11.139 --> 01:04:12.390
Hey.

764
01:04:27.739 --> 01:04:28.948
Hey, look.

765
01:04:29.741 --> 01:04:31.409
We are one.

766
01:04:33.119 --> 01:04:35.914
-What?
-Let's get outta here.

767
01:04:35.997 --> 01:04:40.877
We'll run away together
and start a pride all our own.

768
01:04:42.545 --> 01:04:45.173
Kovu, we have to go back.

769
01:04:45.465 --> 01:04:47.675
You're kidding.
But we're finally together.

770
01:04:48.301 --> 01:04:50.804
Our place is with our pride.

771
01:04:52.097 --> 01:04:56.434
If we run away,
they'll be divided forever.

772
01:05:22.669 --> 01:05:27.132
I can't believe we lost her again.
This is the eight thousandth time!

773
01:05:27.215 --> 01:05:29.801
-I thought you were gonna watch her.
-Me? You were gonna watch her.

774
01:05:29.884 --> 01:05:32.470
-I thought you were gonna watch her.
-No, you were gonna watch her.

775
01:05:32.554 --> 01:05:37.016
-Watch this!
-Take that, you creepy warthog!

776
01:05:37.559 --> 01:05:41.104
-Say it! Say it!
-Fat! Fatty! Fat! Fat!

777
01:05:41.187 --> 01:05:42.689
What are you doing?

778
01:05:43.606 --> 01:05:45.817
Good question. Let me ask you one.

779
01:05:45.942 --> 01:05:48.903
-Hypothetically.
-Very hypothetical.

780
01:05:49.070 --> 01:05:50.780
-There's this guy...
-But he's not a lion.

781
01:05:50.864 --> 01:05:52.824
No! No, he's not a lion.

782
01:05:53.032 --> 01:05:55.034
Definitely not a lion!

783
01:05:55.368 --> 01:05:59.497
And his daughter, say, vanished.

784
01:05:59.664 --> 01:06:00.832
Kiara's gone?

785
01:06:01.166 --> 01:06:03.293
Sire, the Outsiders are on the attack,

786
01:06:03.585 --> 01:06:06.045
heading this way. It's war!

787
01:06:06.212 --> 01:06:09.257
Zazu, find Kiara.
We'll assemble the lionesses.

788
01:06:09.340 --> 01:06:10.800
Move now.

789
01:06:56.095 --> 01:06:58.097
It's over, Simba.

790
01:06:59.057 --> 01:07:03.186
I have dreamed
of nothing else for years.

791
01:07:03.520 --> 01:07:05.188
Does she need a hobby.

792
01:07:05.563 --> 01:07:07.607
Last chance, Zira. Go home.

793
01:07:07.732 --> 01:07:09.776
I am home.

794
01:07:12.654 --> 01:07:13.947
Attack!

795
01:07:28.503 --> 01:07:29.963
Go for the eyes!

796
01:07:30.797 --> 01:07:31.965
Break his jaw!

797
01:07:32.840 --> 01:07:33.967
Hit him low!

798
01:07:34.467 --> 01:07:37.554
Get them! Do what you must!

799
01:07:49.315 --> 01:07:50.441
What do we do? What do we do?

800
01:07:50.858 --> 01:07:52.735
There's only one thing
we can do, Pumbaa.

801
01:07:52.819 --> 01:07:56.990
When the going gets tough,
the tough get going. That's our motto.

802
01:07:57.282 --> 01:08:00.159
I thought our motto was,
<i>"Hakuna matata."</i>

803
01:08:00.243 --> 01:08:02.203
Pumbaa, stop living in the past.

804
01:08:02.453 --> 01:08:03.830
We need a new motto.

805
01:08:09.836 --> 01:08:12.880
Like I said, let's get going!

806
01:08:22.807 --> 01:08:25.977
-Where's your pretty daughter, Nala?
-Vitani!

807
01:08:43.911 --> 01:08:47.832
Don't anybody move.
This thing's loaded. I'll let you have it.

808
01:08:49.751 --> 01:08:50.877
Yeah!

809
01:08:52.754 --> 01:08:54.881
Talk about your winds of war.

810
01:08:57.884 --> 01:08:59.927
Simba.

811
01:09:00.928 --> 01:09:03.389
You're mine.

812
01:09:28.748 --> 01:09:30.416
Kiara?

813
01:09:31.501 --> 01:09:33.002
Kovu!

814
01:09:33.336 --> 01:09:34.962
Move.

815
01:09:35.880 --> 01:09:37.423
Stand aside.

816
01:09:37.882 --> 01:09:39.759
Daddy, this has to stop.

817
01:09:41.427 --> 01:09:45.181
You're even weaker than I thought.
Get out of the way.

818
01:09:45.473 --> 01:09:49.018
You'll never hurt Kiara or Simba.

819
01:09:49.143 --> 01:09:50.895
Not while I'm here.

820
01:09:52.105 --> 01:09:53.523
Stay out of this.

821
01:09:54.107 --> 01:09:57.944
A wise king once told me, "We are one."

822
01:09:58.945 --> 01:10:00.738
I didn't understand him then.

823
01:10:02.115 --> 01:10:03.282
Now I do.

824
01:10:03.491 --> 01:10:05.118
-But they...
-Them?

825
01:10:05.785 --> 01:10:07.954
Us? Look at them.

826
01:10:08.162 --> 01:10:10.373
They are us.

827
01:10:10.456 --> 01:10:13.084
What differences do you see?

828
01:10:37.525 --> 01:10:39.318
Vitani, now!

829
01:10:39.694 --> 01:10:41.654
No, Mother.

830
01:10:44.198 --> 01:10:46.200
Kiara's right.

831
01:10:48.911 --> 01:10:50.496
Enough.

832
01:10:52.498 --> 01:10:54.917
If you will not fight,

833
01:10:55.001 --> 01:10:58.087
then you will die as well.

834
01:11:02.717 --> 01:11:05.011
Where are you going?

835
01:11:05.136 --> 01:11:06.345
Get back here!

836
01:11:06.512 --> 01:11:10.349
Let it go, Zira.
It's time to put the past behind us.

837
01:11:10.516 --> 01:11:13.102
I'll never let it go!

838
01:11:15.605 --> 01:11:17.732
This is for you, Scar!

839
01:11:21.652 --> 01:11:22.945
Kiara!

840
01:11:25.198 --> 01:11:26.324
Kiara!

841
01:11:29.035 --> 01:11:30.077
Kiara!

842
01:11:43.299 --> 01:11:45.176
Hold on, Kiara!

843
01:11:50.598 --> 01:11:51.641
Simba!

844
01:11:52.558 --> 01:11:53.976
Simba, the river!

845
01:12:05.530 --> 01:12:07.740
Zira, give me your paw.

846
01:12:15.081 --> 01:12:16.874
Zira, come on!

847
01:12:19.502 --> 01:12:20.586
I'll help you.

848
01:12:48.239 --> 01:12:50.116
Kiara.

849
01:12:50.199 --> 01:12:51.784
Daddy.

850
01:12:52.660 --> 01:12:53.786
I tried.

851
01:12:56.622 --> 01:12:58.082
Kiara!

852
01:12:59.125 --> 01:13:02.044
Wow! That was really brave!

853
01:13:04.839 --> 01:13:06.382
-Kovu.
-Kiara.

854
01:13:07.967 --> 01:13:08.968
Kovu?

855
01:13:11.053 --> 01:13:14.098
I was wrong. You belong here.

856
01:13:20.646 --> 01:13:22.356
Let's go home.

857
01:13:24.108 --> 01:13:25.651
All of us.

858
01:13:56.557 --> 01:13:59.685
-I love moments like this!
-Yeah.

859
01:14:00.019 --> 01:14:02.355
-Love, not like.
-Love, not like.

860
01:14:02.855 --> 01:14:04.690
-Love!
-Love!

861
01:15:01.664 --> 01:15:04.583
<i>Well done, my son.</i>

862
01:15:14.593 --> 01:15:16.887
<i>We are one.</i>

